  "text": "An exclusive duffel bag and robe from Avicii's 2013 Hotel Miami pop-up are now up for grabs, offering fans a chance to own a piece of EDM history.c/o Pophouse EntertainmentAn exclusive duffel bag and robe from Avicii's 2013 Hotel Miami pop-up are now up for grabs, offering fans a chance to own a piece of EDM history.HomeNEWSIf hotel walls could talk, the Marlin Hotel in Miami would have stories of EDM royalty echoing from every corner. Back in 2013, Avicii famously turned the boutique South Beach property into a living shrine to his music and brand during Miami Music Week. Now, two exclusive relics from that historic takeover—a duffel bag and bathrobe given only to VIP guests at the time—have cropped up in an online auction. Nearly 12 years ago, the late dance music icon transformed the Marlin into the Avicii Hotel, a 16-room fan experience that catered to VIPs and diehard fans flocking to Miami for Ultra Music Festival. The lavish experience included rooms named after his greatest hits, personalized welcome notes, Avicii-themed cocktails, and even branded toiletries.Among the most coveted items from the exclusive event were limited-edition duffel bags and bathrobes provided to guests staying at the hotel.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticleseBayThe bag and robe, each emblazoned with bespoke Avicii branding, were designed as stylish yet functional keepsakes, unmistakably embodying the artist’s signature aesthetic. With only 16 rooms available, the exact number of these items produced remains unknown, but it's safe to say their scarcity only fuels their mystique.The sale comes at a poignant time for Avicii's legacy. Netflix on On New Year's Eve released Avicii – I'm Tim, a deeply personal documentary chronicling the life, struggles and musical genius of the dance music legend. Owning a piece of the late artist's history is akin to holding onto a fragment of a moment that defined the golden era of EDM and celebrated the genius of one of its most beloved artists. The duffel bag and bathrobe are now open for bidding on eBay.Sign up for our NewsletterSign up for the latest news, exclusive giveaways \u0026 more.",
