czMTUzNTQ5OTUy/s-l1600-1.jpg 190w, https://edm.com/.image/ar_100:171%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_310/MjEyMjA3NDczMTUzNTQ5OTUy/s-l1600-1.jpg 310w, https://edm.com/.image/ar_100:171%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_350/MjEyMjA3NDczMTUzNTQ5OTUy/s-l1600-1.jpg 350w, https://edm.com/.image/ar_100:171%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyMjA3NDczMTUzNTQ5OTUy/s-l1600-1.jpg 620w, https://edm.com/.image/ar_100:171%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyMjA3NDczMTUzNTQ5OTUy/s-l1600-1.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"s-l1600 (1)\" height=\"1200\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, calc(50vw - 40px)\" src=\"https://edm.com/.image/ar_100:171%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyMjA3NDczMTUzNTQ5OTUy/s-l1600-1.jpg\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" width=\"1600\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eeBay\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe bag and robe, each emblazoned with bespoke Avicii branding, were designed as stylish yet functional keepsakes, unmistakably embodying the artist’s signature aesthetic. With only 16 rooms available, the exact number of these items produced remains unknown, but it\u0026#39;s safe to say their scarcity only fuels their mystique.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe sale comes at a poignant time for Avicii\u0026#39;s legacy. Netflix on On New Year\u0026#39;s Eve released \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://edm.com/features/inside-netflix-documentary-avicii-im-tim\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eAvicii – I\u0026#39;m Tim\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e, a deeply personal documentary chronicling the life, struggles and musical genius of the dance music legend. Owning a piece of the late artist\u0026#39;s history is akin to holding onto a fragment of a moment that defined the golden era of EDM and celebrated the genius of one of its most beloved artists. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/396123779303\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eduffel bag\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/396123778742\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebathrobe\u003c/a\u003e are now open for bidding on eBay.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phxbrandengagement-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eSign up for our Newsletter\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up for the latest news, exclusive giveaways \u0026amp; more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxstandardtilehub-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-7\"\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://edm.com/.image/cs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good/MTUzMjUyNTA4NzMzNTQ3NTI3/section_header_art_small_related.svg\" alt=\"Related\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-hub data-group-size=\"9\" data-first-group-size=\"9\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-recommendations config=\"{\u0026#34;siteDomain\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;edm.com\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:8,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;tempest_tile-hub_edm_article-page_title-not-found-1-1\u0026#34;}\" percentage_for_personalized_recommendation=\"50\" additional_personalized_slices=\"[]\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-recommendations\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/phoenix-hub\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
